<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: </font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-08-13 21:04:13</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I did this quest at level 27. everything conned green to me. i got real lucky and only had to wait 2 hours before he spawned. As soon as i rooted him 2 smugglers came out of no where and started hitting and backstabbing me. they dont do didnt do much damage but they kept interrupting my spells and made it very difficult to fight. i eventually stunned them both and continued working on the guard and eventually got him and the page! them i promptly killed the 2 smugglers<BR>
for fun. had it been one on one with him i would have beat him like a bongo. lower level peeps might want to harmony or get a higher level friend to help incase the same happens to you. Nice book tho- gives me almost 3 more greater healings in battle!<BR>
<BR>
Spivey Puddledrinker<BR>
Level 31 Cleric<BR>
Tribunal</font></td></tr></table>
